      "description": "FEA-predicted construct stiffness compared against experimental measurements from two independent laboratories. Mean absolute percentage error 4.2%; all 11 specimens within the pre-specified 10% acceptance bound. E/uval ratio 1.31, below the 1.96 threshold. Validation metric satisfies acceptance criteria for stiffness QoI."
    },
    {
