      "name": "Yield force and 40 mm displacement force QoI comparison",
      "description": "FEA-predicted yield force and force at 40 mm displacement compared against experimental results. Mean absolute percentage errors of 6.1% and 5.8% respectively; all specimens within acceptance bounds. E/uval ratios of 1.44 and 1.38. Both QoIs satisfy acceptance criteria. Multi-laboratory concordance strengthens confidence in experimental reference data."
    }
