      "factorType": "Software quality assurance",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical) with documented QA procedures, version control, and regression test suite. Required level 2 for model risk 3 with medium decision consequence.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 used throughout. Vendor-supplied QA documentation, release notes, and benchmark verification suite reviewed and confirmed current. Internal analysis run logs archived with unique job identifiers. Software quality assurance requirements fully satisfied at Gradation 2."
    },
