      "rationale": "Validation activity directly replicates the COU: same device geometry, same test standard (ASTM F1717), same QoIs, same regulatory context. No extrapolation beyond the validated scenario is claimed. Validation activities are maximally relevant to the COU; no gaps identified. Relevance of validation activities to COU fully satisfied."
    }
